Prerequisites:

   c++ compiler (g++ will do perfectly, adapt Makefile if you are using
                 another compiler)
   flex
   bison
   GNU make

In this directory:

   $ make clean
   $ make

Testing:
   
   $ make test

Install findent and the script wfindent in your favorite location, 
for example:

   $ sudo install findent /usr/local/bin
   $ sudo install wfindent /usr/local/bin

The gui front end jfindent:
   install package binfmt-support
   $ install jfindent /usr/local/bin

Create a Windows executable:

   install mingw32

   create findent.exe (windows 32 bit executable):
   $ make clean
   $ make MINGW=1


See also README.1st

USE AT YOUR OWN RISK.
 
